T1  - POLLUTION PERMIT SYSTEMS AND FIRM DYNAMICS: HOW DOES THE ALLOCATION SCHEME MATTER?*
AU  - Dardati, Evangelina
Y1  - 2016/02/01
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2016/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12157
T2  - International Economic Review
